com.microsoft.windowsazure.tracing

Interface CloudTracingInterceptor

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    JavaTracingInterceptor

    public interface CloudTracingInterceptor
    The CloudTracingInterceptor provides useful information about cloud operations. Interception is global and a tracing interceptor can be added via CloudContext.Configuration.Tracing.AddTracingInterceptor.
